Code from the workshop Build Your Own Superhero by CoDesign and Openlab Workshops

http://wiki.openlabworkshops.org/index.php?title=BYOSuperhero

requires Processing from http://processing.org

and the libraries:

SimpleOpenNI - http://code.google.com/p/simple-openni/
GLGraphics library for 3D - http://codeanticode.wordpress.com/libraries/
Toxiclibs - http://toxiclibs.org



